thread.title: Kayla Warner

author: Kayla Warner
title: Kayla Warner
text: This is the first time that I've rented a storage unit and Warren made it an easy and quick transaction. The unit was very clean and safe. There are plenty of security measures to keep your things safe. Warren was very nice and showed how much he cared about his business. I appreciate the fact that he gave me his personal cell number and told me to call him if I had any questions or problems. I would without a doubt recommend going to Warren with any of your storage unit needs.
